      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Spectri Py's compare Spectri Py() and filter Spectri Py() functions allow spectra comparison, and filtering and processing routines, respectively, from the matchms Python library to be called directly from R... Spectri Py provides the functions rspec_to_pyspec() and pyspec_to_rspec() to convert between R's Spectra::Spectra and Python's matchms.Spectrum and spectrum_utils.spectrum.Msms Spectrum objects.",
