      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The open-source Spectri Py R package builds upon reticulate and provides functionality to efficiently translate between R and Python MS data structures. It can convert between R's Spectra::Spectra and Python's matchms.Spectrum and spectrum_utils.spectrum.Msms Spectrum objects and includes functionality to directly apply spectral similarity, filtering, normalization, etc. routines from the Python matchms library on MS data in R.",
