      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "An example combined R-Python data analysis workflow, which can be realized using the Quarto system is provided in the following code snippets. In this particular example we start the analysis in Python, loading and processing the MS data with functions from the matchms library... load_from_mgf(<MGF file>)",
