      "asbval:target_claim_field": "scope",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "When to use: You have mass spectrometry spectral data (m/z and intensity pairs, precursor m/z, MS level, and metadata) in R memory or in a file format (mzML, mzXML, CDF, MGF, MSP), and you need to organize it into a queryable, processable object",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
